♪ Early this morning

58:15.240 --> 58:17.879
♪ when you knocked upon my door

58:22.160 --> 58:24.079
♪ Early this morning

58:26.760 --> 58:29.199
♪ when you knocked upon my door

58:29.800 --> 58:31.679
Don't move!

58:33.520 --> 58:36.279
♪ And I say, hello, Satan

58:38.200 --> 58:39.439
Hello, Mary.

58:39.560 --> 58:41.639
I think you should stay away from me.

